### Register a new user
### Register a new user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "sHASHWAT",
  "email": "stuti@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!",
  "confirm_password": "StrongPass123!"
}

###

### Login (get your JWT tokens)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "sHASHWAT",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

###

### Get profile (paste your access token from login response)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/profile/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzc0ODc0NjUyLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ4NzEwNTIsImp0aSI6IjlhMDlkNmM3ZDljOTQ5NWY4OTRmNzljMjJiMGJlOTY2IiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjMifQ.qpiZKZfT-fbz71qqNOQD1kct4YZ0GYojIznOLNd-0Ko

